1. *Prvih* nekoliko stranica knjige mi se nije svidjelo. (I didn't like the *first* few pages of the book.)
2. U *prvih* nekoliko mjeseci veze smo bili jako zaljubljeni. (We were very much in love in the *first* few months of our relationship.)
3. *Prvih* pet studenata koji se prijave na izlet, dobit će besplatnu kartu. (The *first* five students who sign up for the trip will get a free ticket.)
4. Kupila sam *prvih* deset knjiga iz te serije i jedva čekam da pročitam sve. (I bought the *first* ten books from that series and I can't wait to read them all.)
5. *Prvih* nekoliko minuta predavanja su bila dosadna, ali onda je profesor postao zanimljiviji. (The *first* few minutes of the lecture were boring, but then the professor became more interesting.)
6. Učenici su *prvih* nekoliko zadataka riješili brzo, ali onda su se zapetljali u složenije zadatke. (The students solved the *first* few tasks quickly, but then they got tangled up in more complex tasks.)
7. Saznala sam da će *prvih* pet dana na putovanju biti kišovito, pa sam ponijela kišobran. (I found out that it will be rainy for the *first* five days of the trip, so I brought an umbrella.)
8. *Prvih* nekoliko godina karijere mi je bilo teško, ali onda sam se ustalila. (The *first* few years of my career were difficult, but then I settled in.)
9. Prijatelj mi je posudio *prvih* sto stranica svoje knjige, a ja sam mu obećala da ću je pročitati. (My friend lent me the *first* hundred pages of his book, and I promised him that I would read it.)
10. U *prvih* nekoliko tjedana pandemije, mnogi su bili u panici, ali onda se situacija malo smirila. (In the *first* few weeks of the pandemic, many people were in panic, but then the situation calmed down a bit.)